Oh, no, Detectives, sir!

503
00:47:14,280 --> 00:47:17,000
I will make mincemeat out of him with my own hands!

504
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:19,730
Oh, President, what's the matter with you?

505
00:47:20,430 --> 00:47:24,710
Just in case he comes this way, I'm saying it so he will hear.

506
00:47:24,710 --> 00:47:27,460
Where else would that soft-hearted kid be able to go?

507
00:47:27,460 --> 00:47:32,130
If perhaps he's hanging around, he shouldn't get caught.

508
00:47:32,130 --> 00:47:34,270
You son of a bitch!

509
00:47:38,680 --> 00:47:41,360
Detectives, you've gone through a lot of trouble since the official documents.

510
00:47:41,360 --> 00:47:44,650
How about a serving of steamed eggs on the house?

511
00:47:44,650 --> 00:47:46,240
No, that's okay.

512
00:47:46,240 --> 00:47:49,920
All right.  Take your time. Eat a lot.

513
00:47:51,580 --> 00:47:55,700
 Yook Dong Sik Get out of here murderer! 
 Go Bankrupt!

514
00:47:57,070 --> 00:48:02,530
 There is only one person who can help me.

515
00:48:08,170 --> 00:48:10,520
 Officer Heo

516
00:48:11,450 --> 00:48:12,950
Yes. Tell me.

517
00:48:12,960 --> 00:48:15,930
 The CCTVs in all the crucial locations were out of order.

518
00:48:15,930 --> 00:48:18,410
And on those that were normally functioning, he didn't leave any trace at all.

519
00:48:18,410 --> 00:48:22,140
Wow.  The guy is really meticulous.

520
00:48:22,140 --> 00:48:24,090
Was my car checked too?

521
00:48:24,090 --> 00:48:26,050
 Yes.  It was wiped spotless.

522
00:48:26,050 --> 00:48:29,230
No DNA, fingerprints, nothing.

523
00:48:30,820 --> 00:48:31,960
What about Dong Sik?

524
00:48:31,960 --> 00:48:36,530
In contrast to the meticulous guy, he was captured here and there on CCTV.

525
00:48:36,530 --> 00:48:41,150
It seems like he is in Seoul, but we still don't have an exact location.

526
00:48:41,150 --> 00:48:46,180
If he came to Seoul, it means he wants to reveal the truth.

527
00:48:46,180 --> 00:48:48,170
Maybe he is trying to meet you

528
00:48:48,170 --> 00:48:52,110
since you are the only person Dong Sik can trust.

529
00:48:52,110 --> 00:48:55,620
You've worked hard.  For now, come here.

530
00:48:57,590 --> 00:49:02,440
 Dong Sik... wants to meet me?

531
00:49:03,250 --> 00:49:06,420
Hello, Sunbae.  Good morning!

532
00:49:08,710 --> 00:49:10,120
Don't tell me you stayed here all night!

533
00:49:10,120 --> 00:49:13,670
Impenetrable! I'm fine!

534
00:49:13,670 --> 00:49:16,340
Just take it easy.

535
00:49:16,340 --> 00:49:19,650
  At Naksan-dong intersection, there is a witness report of a person presumed to be Yook Dong Sik.

536
00:49:19,650 --> 00:49:24,150
  Disheveled hair, dressed like a farmworker. Mobile patrol in the vicinity please check.

537
00:49:24,150 --> 00:49:26,220
That's right in front.

538
00:49:26,220 --> 00:49:28,440
I'll go take a look. You stay here for a second.

539
00:49:28,440 --> 00:49:32,280
Where are you going? Sunbae, you stay put.

540
00:49:32,280 --> 00:49:33,740
But ...

541
00:49:33,740 --> 00:49:35,680
 Boring Day

542
00:49:41,860 --> 00:49:44,860
 The predator is closer than I thought.

543
00:49:44,860 --> 00:49:49,570
 If I am to catch him, I need to see Bo Gyeong somehow.

544
00:49:58,850 --> 00:50:00,720
Where is Yook Dong Sik?

545
00:50:00,720 --> 00:50:03,750
Hey! Put your gun away.

546
00:50:09,030 --> 00:50:11,820
Oh. There! There!

547
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:26,500
Yook Dong Sik!

548
00:51:05,250 --> 00:51:07,280
 We just received breaking news.

549
00:51:07,280 --> 00:51:12,210
 Yook Dong Sik, on the run since escaping from prison, was spotted in the middle of Seoul.

550
00:51:12,210 --> 00:51:16,400
 He still seems to be targeting the officer who arrested him,

551
00:51:16,400 --> 00:51:18,840
 and he was almost caught through a citizen's report.

552
00:51:18,840 --> 00:51:24,520
 But in the end, he's continuing his escape after shaking off the police pursuit.

553
00:51:38,320 --> 00:51:41,060
First, listen to wh-what I have to say.

554
00:51:41,060 --> 00:51:44,040
To tell you the truth, what happened is—

555
00:51:44,040 --> 00:51:48,090
When you are on the run, it's best not to stand out.

556
00:51:48,090 --> 00:51:52,120
What's with those clothes?  What's with the baggy pants?

557
00:51:55,530 --> 00:51:58,350
Put these on.

558
00:51:58,350 --> 00:52:02,980
Whether you came out through the front or the back door, you're out of prison now,

559
00:52:03,900 --> 00:52:06,230
so take a bite of this first.

560
00:52:06,930 --> 00:52:10,580
 (T.N. Released prisoners traditionally eat tofu.  The white of tofu symbolizes purity.)

561
00:52:14,010 --> 00:52:15,510
You didn't eat, did you?

562
00:52:15,510 --> 00:52:17,870
This. This.

563
00:52:17,870 --> 00:52:21,750
Choco-Pie, bread, these, eat everything!

564
00:52:27,780 --> 00:52:30,130
Chil Seong...

565
00:52:32,430 --> 00:52:35,170
Move over a little.

566
00:52:45,030 --> 00:52:49,070
I mean, it's not like you're fool. Why did you go there?

567
00:52:49,070 --> 00:52:51,900
There are tons of cops there.

568
00:52:53,000 --> 00:52:55,700
You're lucky I was on standby.

569
00:52:55,700 --> 00:52:59,920
Bo Gyeong is the only person I can trust.

570
00:53:00,950 --> 00:53:07,250
What about me? Did you think I would be-betray you ?

571
00:53:07,250 --> 00:53:09,350
We're brothers.

572
00:53:19,360 --> 00:53:22,180
Chil Seong...

573
00:53:23,990 --> 00:53:26,510
Such a fool!

574
00:53:26,510 --> 00:53:29,310
Don't cry.

575
00:53:29,310 --> 00:53:31,720
I'm sorry.

576
00:53:32,750 --> 00:53:35,300
Chil Seong, I'm sorry.

577
00:53:40,250 --> 00:53:42,360
How did you let him get away?!

578
00:53:43,200 --> 00:53:44,230
What did the station say?

579
00:53:44,230 --> 00:53:49,660
Yes, they're deploying additional personnel to the district and doubling their patrols in the area.

580
00:53:50,600 --> 00:53:54,640
Anyway, Yook Dong Sik must be holding a strong grudge.

581
00:53:54,640 --> 00:53:58,000
Trying to enter into the very tiger's den!

582
00:53:59,020 --> 00:54:02,400
- We had a situation, so...  
 - You're talking about a situation?

583
00:54:04,400 --> 00:54:07,880
  A Boring Day

584
00:54:12,290 --> 00:54:15,850
But... you're under such tight observation.

585
00:54:15,850 --> 00:54:19,930
Could there be a way we could secretly have contact with him?

586
00:54:19,930 --> 00:54:23,950
Like at a place only the two of you would know, for example.

587
00:54:23,950 --> 00:54:26,140
You're right.

588
00:54:32,060 --> 00:54:34,840
Wait a minute.

589
00:54:34,840 --> 00:54:36,770
That 'beard'!

590
00:54:36,770 --> 00:54:39,720
Why am I so happy to see that?

591
00:54:44,820 --> 00:54:46,880
Ah! I've got a cramp!

592
00:54:46,880 --> 00:54:49,800
Got a cramp!

593
00:54:51,210 --> 00:54:54,720
That's so much like you, Hyungnim. That's so you.

594
00:54:54,720 --> 00:54:59,560
Even after you've figured out my identity, you still call me Hyungnim.

595
00:54:59,560 --> 00:55:04,560
Well, once a Hyungnim, always a Hyungnim.

596
00:55:07,410 --> 00:55:11,190
Still. Weren't you following me around because you thought I was a tough guy?

597
00:55:11,190 --> 00:55:15,000
That's so childish. As if you're a child.

598
00:55:17,140 --> 00:55:21,950
To be honest, I may look like a complete thug, but my fist is too soft.

599
00:55:21,950 --> 00:55:25,060
That's why I was known as 
Beomil-dong's Water Fist 
   ('Water fist' is a way of saying a person is weak at fighting)

600
00:55:25,060 --> 00:55:30,470
You see, a slight punch like this should be enough to kill them.

601
00:55:30,470 --> 00:55:33,720
But throwing a punch like this makes my fist go like this...

602
00:55:35,310 --> 00:55:39,090
And the hit is as gentle as a facial for the opponent.

603
00:55:39,090 --> 00:55:42,330
That's why ... I was too embarrassed.

604
00:55:42,330 --> 00:55:45,840
Do you know what I tell my guys?

605
00:55:45,840 --> 00:55:50,910
I don't use my fist unless it's for something righteous.

606
00:55:54,090 --> 00:55:56,010
I'm sorry.

607
00:55:56,010 --> 00:55:59,800
It's nothing. Everyone laughed at me like that.

608
00:56:01,350 --> 00:56:07,250
We're living in a time where you must be able to backstab your family as well as your brothers to succeed.

609
00:56:07,250 --> 00:56:12,870
So that's why I was wondering whether I should leave this field. And, klop!

610
00:56:12,870 --> 00:56:20,130
I met you. Strong to the strong and knows how to care for the weak, a real chivalrous fighter.

611
00:56:20,130 --> 00:56:24,170
But I'm telling you, I was like that because I thought I was the Predator.

612
00:56:24,170 --> 00:56:26,920
Hyungnim. Real strength,

613
00:56:26,920 --> 00:56:29,500
does not come from there,

614
00:56:32,370 --> 00:56:34,430
but from right here.

615
00:56:34,430 --> 00:56:36,840
Just like you.

616
00:56:38,550 --> 00:56:43,560
But anyway, we have to meet Corporal— I mean Sergeant Sim.

617
00:56:43,560 --> 00:56:46,470
Should I secretly try to contact her?

618
00:56:46,470 --> 00:56:49,570
The police watch is too strong, it will be dangerous.

619
00:56:49,570 --> 00:56:54,880
And didn't you say you were even investigated as an accomplice?

620
00:56:54,880 --> 00:56:57,140
So that only Sergeant Sim will know.

621
00:56:57,140 --> 00:57:01,110
could there be a way to secretly leave a message for her?

622
00:57:28,210 --> 00:57:32,660
Where was the light switch again?

623
00:57:33,670 --> 00:57:35,570
Just a moment.

624
00:57:42,530 --> 00:57:48,780
Hyungnim, after you were arrested, rumors spread that this was where a killer practiced his murders.

625
00:57:51,110 --> 00:57:52,740
Why did we come here again?

626
00:57:52,740 --> 00:57:57,890
You've just escaped the prison. Why are you trying to escape another room?

627
00:57:58,710 --> 00:58:00,670
Are you hooked?

628
00:58:00,670 --> 00:58:05,580
If Bo Gyeong were looking for me and trying to contact me in some way,

629
00:58:05,580 --> 00:58:09,080
I thought she would come by here at least once.

630
00:58:22,600 --> 00:58:24,710
A perfect crime.

631
00:58:44,240 --> 00:58:48,900
I think that if I were to leave a message here, Bo Gyeong might see it.

632
00:59:15,760 --> 00:59:19,260
  January 2nd, 14:00. Seorim Park.

633
00:59:19,260 --> 00:59:24,380
I was right. She had the same thought.

634
00:59:30,360 --> 00:59:32,110
  A Boring Day

635
00:59:32,110 --> 00:59:33,620
A walk?

636
00:59:33,620 --> 00:59:38,110
My father seems stifled being cooped up in the house. We'll just go get some air.

637
00:59:38,110 --> 00:59:40,550
- But the situation at hand is not good. 
 - Hey!

638
00:59:40,550 --> 00:59:42,070
Yes?

639
00:59:42,900 --> 00:59:48,080
I'm going to go with her, so please stop worrying, I beg you!

640
00:59:48,080 --> 00:59:50,310
But the situation at hand is not good!

641
00:59:50,310 --> 00:59:52,670
You, really..

642
00:59:59,680 --> 01:00:02,120
Sunbae, I'll stay here and keep watch.

643
01:00:02,120 --> 01:00:03,790
Okay.

644
01:00:21,420 --> 01:00:23,490
Taek Soo!

645
01:00:28,170 --> 01:00:30,400
Please take my father with you.

646
01:00:50,840 --> 01:00:53,060
Dong Sik!

647
01:01:00,950 --> 01:01:03,060
Bo Gyeong!

648
01:01:08,430 --> 01:01:10,780
What were you thinking, breaking out of prison?

649
01:01:10,780 --> 01:01:12,400
The thing is that ...

650
01:01:12,400 --> 01:01:16,770
Death threat? Do you know how much things have gotten worse because of that?

651
01:01:16,770 --> 01:01:21,740
I had no other choice. I was afraid something bad would happen to you.

652
01:01:23,540 --> 01:01:26,660
Why is your hit so painful? Gosh.

653
01:01:32,000 --> 01:01:34,600
You're insane, really.

654
01:01:34,600 --> 01:01:38,320
Why do all that for me?

655
01:01:38,320 --> 01:01:42,970
Still, I'm glad you're okay.

656
01:01:47,740 --> 01:01:51,780
I'm sorry. Because of me ...

657
01:01:51,780 --> 01:01:56,330
you were arrested and even broke out of jail.

658
01:01:57,600 --> 01:02:01,820
Thanks to you, I was able to get away from that terrible delusion.

659
01:02:06,690 --> 01:02:11,790
Since things have ended up like this, let's make sure to catch the real culprit

660
01:02:11,790 --> 01:02:13,690
with our own hands.

661
01:02:17,170 --> 01:02:21,190
But then again, it's what we've been doing since before.

662
01:02:21,190 --> 01:02:25,730
It's the two of us who know best about the predator.

663
01:02:32,420 --> 01:02:35,000
Anyway, it's so like you.

664
01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:38,710
How did you come up with the idea of how to contact me?

665
01:02:42,490 --> 01:02:47,170
You said we should meet here.

666
01:02:47,170 --> 01:02:50,150
At the escape cafe room.

667
01:02:51,200 --> 01:02:57,590
What? Weren't you the one who left that note?

668
01:02:59,410 --> 01:03:01,540
Hyungnim.

669
01:03:12,490 --> 01:03:15,890
What again?  What should I do?

670
01:03:40,650 --> 01:03:42,310
Yes.

671
01:03:51,560 --> 01:03:53,780
Then this is ...

672
01:03:55,230 --> 01:03:57,280
It's a trap.

673
01:04:01,490 --> 01:04:05,710
 Psychopath Diary

674
01:04:07,940 --> 01:04:14,900

675
01:04:16,710 --> 01:04:18,170
 The memory was evoked. In a flash.

676
01:04:18,170 --> 01:04:21,750
  You're the only one I can ask for help now.

677
01:04:21,750 --> 01:04:23,210
 Where are you?  I'll go to you.

678
01:04:23,210 --> 01:04:27,970
 Right. It wouldn't be all that bad to meet your fate while running away frightened.

679
01:04:27,970 --> 01:04:30,540
 Sergeant Sim, something bad happened again!

680
01:04:30,540 --> 01:04:34,350
  Dong Sik figured out who the real killer is.

681
01:04:34,350 --> 01:04:37,850
  Dong Sik and I will make sure we capture him. 
  Evil Nightmare

682
01:04:37,850 --> 01:04:42,150
  Will you be able to pierce through the bodysuit with a dull knife that only looks like the real thing?

683
01:04:42,150 --> 01:04:45,950
  I will get you yet, Seo In Woo.
